    MultiPrecision<ImgLinearSubnetLayer>, Layer, ReferenceCounting, Serializable

    public class ImgLinearSubnetLayer
extends LayerBase
implements MultiPrecision<ImgLinearSubnetLayer>
    This key works as a scaling function, similar to a father wavelet. Allows convolutional and pooling layers to work across larger png regions.
